title: Ep - 3 - Matt Anderson and Nate Green of Purveyors of Pop
description:
Kate interviews Matt Anderson and Nate Green with Purveyors of
Pop about what they look for when casting reality show personalities, her
friend Ashley gives a review of Finding Prince Charming, and she asks her
friend Lindsay¹s husband Fritz for his commentary regarding Married at
First Sight.
